        "content": "<p>The first line says that a continuous function (on an interval) is also integrable on that interval, so it suffices to prove continuity. <code>fun_prop</code> is a tactic that proves <em>prop</em>erties of <em>fun</em>ctions (in particular properties that can be proved in a straightforward way by looking at the structure of the function), and continuity is one of those properties</p>",
